Ryo, the CF's external defences are completely destroyed, its hull is 
full of holes, although only one is big enough to let bots through and 
I think its covered up, and the power source is dying from 
overworking.

::Prowl::

Prowl watches Angel Prime give Iron Raptor the Matrix and smiles. Not 
she would be a true leader. He just hoped the Matrix was enough to 
lead them through to survival, possibly even victory. 
-Congratulations, love!- he thinks to her.

He frowns at SilverBolt. The bot was definetly oversimplifying the 
damage of the Cybertronian Fire.

"Its more than just not in good shape," he says, looking at the CF, 
and then to Iron Raptor, "Its starting to look like the Ark did."
